      <p>[Draw tree here]</p>

      <p>d) Complex sentence: <foreign>When it rained, we stayed inside.</foreign></p>
      <tabular top="minor" left="minor">
        <col halign="left" right="minor"/>
        <col halign="center" right="minor"/>
        <col halign="center" right="minor"/>
